      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TSUNAMI SEA (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (19.39) at Q Straight. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Can make amends. STRIKING BEACH (4) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at Rockhampton over 407m behind Tough One (24.73) in a Grade 6. Was in the money the start prior. Should be thereabouts. TARCISIA (2) recorded her best time this course and distance last start, taking a Maiden in 20.28 by 0.8 lengths. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. MY MINUET (7) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
